@333 =~Amber left <CHARNAME> right after the events at the Throne of Bhaal. The experience in the Abyss and with its creatures had shown her that she still did not know who she was and which was the life she wanted to live. She went to search for Cadderly, the human she had learned to be her father.

What exactly happened between father and daughter after she reached Spirit Soaring will remain their common secret. Anyway, Amber decided to stay at that place of healing and became part of the community around her father without but without becoming a priest herself.

Her magnificent fighting skills were tested at several times during assaults made on the temple. She became Spirit Soaring's main defender by those events. She and <CHARNAME> never met again.~